&lt;h2&gt;Profound vs. AthenaHQ AI for AEO: At a glance&lt;/h2&gt; 
&lt;a&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;h2&gt;Profound vs. AthenaHQ compared&lt;/h2&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;Here’s a breakdown of some key features of both Profound and AthenaHQ, and how each &lt;a href="https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/generative-engine-optimization-tools"&gt;GEO tool&lt;/a&gt; handles the feature.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;h3&gt;Monitoring vs. Action&lt;/h3&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;One of the biggest differentiators between Profound and Athena AI in the AEO comparison is the primary problem each tool solves.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;Profound is an AEO platform for monitoring and analytics. It includes a visibility intelligence command center where data from multiple engines gets synthesized into competitive insight.&lt;/p&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;Here’s a screenshot showing what the monitoring analytics looks like. The screenshot shows a graph with referral traffic from AI systems in one place. SEO experts can use this graph to identify the AI agents working best for the business, and those with the greatest opportunity:&lt;/p&gt; 
