&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Which platform wins?&lt;/strong&gt; Both platforms are excellent for monitoring, but AthenaHQ offers the added value of the Action Center, which helps teams turn insights into actions. The best tool depends on team needs and existing capabilities. Teams whose SEO staff can identify actions from analytics will find Profound a strong fit. Teams that need support with briefs and next steps will find AthenaHQ the more guided option.&lt;/p&gt; 
