 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#do-you-need-brand-optimization"&gt;Do you need brand optimization?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#how-to-optimize-your-brand-brand-optimization-checklist-and-strategy"&gt;How to Optimize Your Brand: Brand Optimization Checklist and Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#how-to-measure-success-from-brand-optimization"&gt;How to Measure Success from Brand Optimization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
 &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#frequently-asked-questions-about-brand-optimization"&gt;Frequently asked questions about brand optimization&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; 
